summary: Basic attestation scenario via MCP server
description: |
    Tests MCP protocol initialization, tool listing,
    health check, agent enrollment, status and unenrollment
    against a running keylime instance.
contact: Marek Safarik <msafarik@redhat.com>
component:
  - keylime-mcp
framework: shell
test: go test -v -tags=functional .
require:
  - golang
  - keylime
duration: 5m
enabled: true
